      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop your <strong>shallots</strong> in half</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and discard the skins</p><p>Once the dish is hot, add your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
