    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved shallots</strong> and <strong>peeled garlic</strong> with your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add 350ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [455ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[650ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, your<strong> red wine paste </strong>and <strong>beef stock mix</strong></p><p>Crumble in your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
