      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, add your <strong>bay leaf[ves]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>and <strong>dried<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>thyme</strong></p><p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 40 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>coq au vin</strong></p>",
