      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's ready, remove the potatoes from the oven and crush them firmly with a spatula or the bottom of a plate</p><p>Add a couple of knobs of <strong>butter</strong> and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix it all together – these are your <strong>buttery crushed potatoes</strong></p>",
